Global Dry Mouth Remedies Market Insights
Dry Mouth Remedies Market size was valued at USD 3.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.


Dry Mouth Remedies Market Overview
The global Dry Mouth Remedies market has been growing steadily, with a projected market value of USD 1.1 billion by 2025, reflecting a substantial increase in demand for treatments addressing xerostomia, or dry mouth. This growth is primarily driven by increasing awareness of oral health, rising incidences of health conditions like diabetes, and a growing elderly population. Additionally, advancements in dry mouth management solutions have led to more targeted and effective treatment options, thus expanding market potential. The market includes various remedies such as mouthwashes, lozenges, sprays, and oral gels.

